    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains crisp. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for chassis longevity. The suspension retains its communicative geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity is prioritized. A true enthusiast's machine with a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and exceptional throttle response.",
