    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a stunning 2017 BMW M2 finished in iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic over a black Dakota leather interior with blue contrast stitching. This vehicle has been adult-owned and meticulously maintained, showing the pride of ownership through every mile. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six delivers a visceral driving experience, paired with a crisp 7-speed M Double-Clutch Transmission. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though it shows a few light stone chips on the front fascia consistent with spirited weekend drives. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the carbon fiber trim is flawless, and the heated sport seats show only minor softening on the driver-side bolster. All electronics, from the iDrive navigation to the Harman Kardon premium sound system, function perfectly. Recently serviced with a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, this M2 sits on Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with plenty of tread remaining. Includes two keys, original floor mats, and a comprehensive folder of service records. This is a turn-key performance machine ready for its next enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
